maxflow
------------------------------------------
Software for computing mincut/maxflow in a graph

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libmaxflow-devel-3.0.5-1bl2
  libmaxflow1-3.0.5-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/gerddie/maxflow

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/gerddie/maxflow/archive/refs/tags/3.0.5.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack maxflow-3.0.5-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./maxflow-3.0.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/maxflow-3.0.5-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/maxflow-3.0.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmaxflow1-3.0.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmaxflow-devel-3.0.5-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(maxflow)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/maxflow.README
  /usr/share/doc/maxflow/CHANGES.TXT
  /usr/share/doc/maxflow/GPL.TXT
  /usr/share/doc/maxflow/README.md

(libmaxflow1)
  /usr/bin/cygmaxflow-1.dll

(libmaxflow-devel)
  /usr/include/maxflow-3.0/maxflow.h
  /usr/include/maxflow-3.0/maxflow/block.h
  /usr/include/maxflow-3.0/maxflow/graph.cpp
  /usr/include/maxflow-3.0/maxflow/graph.h
  /usr/lib/libmaxflow.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/maxflow.pc

------------------

